Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE Ottawa Land Services Group is pleased to offer for sale a significant parcel of land near the City of Ottawa’s Orleans area. This 65 acre property is located adjacent to existing estate lot residential developments, with easy access to major residential and retail developments, public transit along Innes Road, and then on to Highway 174. The Property consists of tile drained farmland and wooded lot with combined frontage of approximately 2,199 feet along French Hill Road and 985 feet on O’Toole Road. This very scenic property is zoned AG2 (Agricultural), providing a variety of options to different buyers with the opportunity to build country home and have farm income- excellent opportunity for owner users or investors alike.

The property is zoned RC( Rural Commercial Zoning) opening up the possibilities for commercial use to serve the public. Listing Price is $420,000 per acre.
